WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Hi, I'm A Poorna Seshaseyan.

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:07.000
I'm an AI and Full Stack Developer passionate about building intelligent systems...

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:08.500
...that solve real-world problems.

00:00:08.500 --> 00:00:12.000
I've built an AI-powered hospital system that enables voice registration...

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:15.000
...and symptom analysis, making healthcare more accessible.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:18.000
I've also developed ML platforms for plant disease detection...

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:22.000
...helping farmers identify crop issues early to protect their yield.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:24.000
And I'm working on AI-driven crowd management systems...

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:27.000
...designed to improve safety during large public gatherings.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:30.000
My strengths lie in Machine Learning, Cloud Computing...

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:34.000
...and building scalable applications that create a real impact.

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:36.000
But what truly drives me is this vision:

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:38.000
Technology should not just be smart,

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:40.000
it should be meaningful and improve lives.

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:43.000
I'm pushing boundaries to create solutions that matter.

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:45.000
Let's build the future with intelligence.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:47.000
This is just the beginning.
